Apmēram četru minūšu laikā jūs

00:11:22.260 --> 00:11:24.260
esat tikuši cipariski saglabāti.

00:11:24.260 --> 00:11:26.260
(Smiekli)

00:11:26.260 --> 00:11:30.260
Vēlos pateikties šiem burvjiem.

00:11:30.260 --> 00:11:33.260
Mums ir ļoti paveicies,

00:11:33.260 --> 00:11:37.260
ka divi no mūsu sadarbības partneriem ir:

00:11:37.260 --> 00:11:39.260
„Historic Scotland“

00:11:39.260 --> 00:11:42.260
un Glāzgovas mākslas skola.

00:11:42.260 --> 00:11:46.260
Es vēlētos arī personīgi pateikties

00:11:46.260 --> 00:11:50.260
par pūliņiem Deividam Mičelam,

00:11:50.260 --> 00:11:53.260
kurš ir Historic Scotland saglabāšanas

00:11:53.260 --> 00:11:55.260
nodaļas direktors.

00:11:55.260 --> 00:11:57.260
Deivid.

00:11:57.260 --> 00:12:00.260
(Aplausi)

00:12:02.260 --> 00:12:04.260
Un Dagam Pričardam, kurš ir Glāzgovas

00:12:04.260 --> 00:12:07.260
mākslas skolas vizualizācijas nodaļas direktors.

00:12:07.260 --> 00:12:09.260
Sniegsim palīdzīgu roku.

00:12:09.260 --> 00:12:12.260
(Aplausi)

00:12:12.260 --> 00:12:15.260
Paldies.

